Interface ResponseHeaders

All Superinterfaces:
HttpHeaders, HttpObject, Iterable<Map.Entry<AsciiString,​String>>
public interface ResponseHeaders
extends HttpHeaders
Immutable HTTP/2 headers for an HttpResponse.

HttpHeaders, RequestHeaders
